When suggesting or writing code for this project, follow these guidelines:

COLOR SYSTEM

- Reference src/colors.css for all color variables
- Never use raw hex codes or RGB values
- Follow the established pattern of using --color-chrome variables for UI chrome elements and --color-content variables for content areas
- Check colors.css for the complete set of available color variables and their intended usage
- Avoid making up or using any CSS variables without checking colors.css first.
- Add new colors variables if needed, and be sure to note the new color in your output.

TYPOGRAPHY

- Reference src/typography.css for all typography-related variables
- Use the established font size, weight, and line height variables defined in typography.css
- Follow the existing font family configuration
- Do not introduce new typography values without checking typography.css first.
- Avoid making up or using any CSS variables without checking typography.css first.

COMPONENT STRUCTURE

- Components should be in their own directory under src/components
- Use PascalCase for component names
- Each component should have:
  - ComponentName.jsx
  - ComponentName.module.css
- Use CSS Modules for styling
- Import styles as: import styles from './ComponentName.module.css'
- Review existing components for patterns and best practices
- Only change code if you're sure you need to

CSS PRACTICES

- Reference existing component CSS files for structural patterns
- Follow the layout patterns established in App.module.css for page structure
- Match the spacing and layout patterns found in existing component CSS modules
- When creating new styles, check similar existing components for consistent patterns

IMPORTS

- Core CSS files should be imported in main.jsx only
- Component CSS modules should only be imported in their respective components

ACCESSIBILITY

- Maintain semantic HTML structure
- Follow heading hierarchy patterns found in existing components
- Ensure proper contrast by using the color system variables appropriately

ICONS

- Use SVG icons for all icons
- Icons should be in their own directory under src/icons
- Icon files should be named IconName.jsx
